    <note>Zhang(1) Hui(6) [10587] A literary scholar who transmitted his teachings to his son, Xiaokai [10588]. One wife [probably #2], born Cao, was the widow of Lin(1) Ximeng [20962] and mother of Lin(1) Songsun [20963], who remarried Zhang Hui and was the mother of Xiaokai. See documentation for Lin(1) Shi(3) [20960]. The father-in-law of his first wife, born Shen [daughter of Du(2) [20937], was also the father-in-law of his second wife's first husband's elder brother. CBD, 3, 2296.</note>
